  "description": "Quarantine Sleep Cell is a narrow sleeping chamber partitioned from the apartment’s central passage by a pressure-rated bulkhead and gasketed frame. A built-in bunk recess and fold-down utility shelf are cast directly into the ribbed ferrocrete wall, minimizing exposed surfaces and loose furnishings. Armored lumen strips behind diffusers maintain a constant, clinical illumination that flattens shadows and erases any sense of night. Vent grilles and sealed conduit runs dominate the upper corners, emphasizing air-control and contamination discipline over comfort.",
